### WhatsApp Gateway API Testing
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 2. Get Connection Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status

### 3. Get QR Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/qr

### 4. Send Single Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "081234567890",
  "message": "Halo, ini pesan test dari SPMB WhatsApp Gateway"
}

### 5. Send Bulk Messages
POST {{baseUrl}}/send-bulk
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "phone": "081234567890",
      "message": "Halo Budi, pendaftaran Anda berhasil. No. Registrasi: REG2026001"
    },
    {
      "phone": "081234567891",
      "message": "Halo Ani, pendaftaran Anda berhasil. No. Registrasi: REG2026002"
    }
  ]
}

### 6. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
